# Replace the IP with YOUR machine's local network IP
#
# Find it:
#   macOS / Linux : ifconfig | grep "inet " | grep -v 127
#   Windows       : ipconfig | findstr IPv4
#
# Android Emulator (AVD) → use 10.0.2.2 instead of localhost
# Physical device         → use your LAN IP, e.g. 192.168.1.100
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

